columns.description: This column was automatically created in order to record in what polygon from the dataset 'Hamilton County Census Tracts - 2010' (c8ia-b5u2) the point in column 'geolocation' is located.  This enables the creation of region maps (choropleths) in the visualization canvas and data lens.
